[224771]="Dealing damage with a <<1>> grants you <<2>> for <<3>>. \r\n\r\nWhile you have <<2>>, your Light Attacks deals an additional <<4>> and <<5>>% more damage to enemies below <<6>>% Health, and your <<1>>s deal an additional <<7>> to your enemy and nearby enemies.\r\n\r\nThese effects scale off Weapon or Spell damage and deal an additional <<8>> more damage per Draconic Power ability slotted, up to 30%.",
[224808]="While in combat, your Light Attacks deals an additional <<1>> and <<2>>% more damage to enemies below <<3>>% Health, and your <<4>>s deal an additional <<5>> to your enemy and enemies near them.\r\n\r\nThese effects scale off Weapon or Spell damage and deal an additional <<6>> more damage per Draconic Power ability slotted, up to 30%.",
