[242055]="Create a corridor of shadows, dealing <<1>> to enemies in the target area every <<2>>.\r\n\r\nWhile on the path and for up to <<3>> after leaving it you gain Major Expedition, increasing your movement speed by <<4>>.",
[242321]="You gain a <<1>>% Experience Point bonus from all sources for <<2>>. Additionally your wayshrine travel cost is reduced <<1>>% . The timer pauses when you are offline, and resumes when you return.",
